COMING SOON!!!

Eight years ago we were two new, young moms looking for a fun hobby that we were passionate about. And so, The Stockplace was born. We had no idea what we were doing but we slowly learned through trial and error. There were lots of mistakes, lots of successes, a few tears, and a lot of laughs. Through the amazing support and love of our customers, our little hobby grew. About two years in we started to dabble in the dream of designing our own pieces. It was AMAZING! We had dresses, jumpsuits, and even swimwear. But as our business grew, so did our families. We made the hard choice to put a pause on designing and manufacturing to focus on our families while our babies were little.  Now that our kids are a little older, we are back to pursing our passions. We’ve put so much time, energy, and love into these dresses and we hope you love them as much as we do! Here’s to chasing big dreams!! Launching 9.13.23

Stockplace the Label launches tomorrow!!! We couldn’t be more proud of our designs and more humbled by the response we’ve had to them! Thank you! Not only are these dresses beautiful, but they’re flattering, comfortable, forgiving and size inclusive!!! Shop them tomorrow morning on our app at 10 am mdt and then on our website at 12 pm mdt!!

Stockplace The Label is Live!!! Thank you from the bottom of our hearts for loving these dresses like we do. We’ve both tried on all three dresses for you. Spoiler alert… they all work on a full term baby bump!

When we were photographing all the looks the other day, we reminisced about our very first collab SEVEN years ago! 

We were both into our business about a year and they asked if I’d teach a demo class at their pop-up shop. It was a huge success and the rest is history! 

We’ve designed dresses together, curated collections together and cheered each other on through the growing pains of business and life. 

I have loved watching Megan and Brynlee do amazing things and am just so grateful all these years later, we’re still in it together 🩷
